    <detaileddescription>
<para>This is a <ref refid="classSharedFinfo" kindref="compound">SharedFinfo</ref>, which wraps an arbitrary set of regular Src and Dest Messages. Its main job is to do typechecking for setting up multiple data streams to go across the same <ref refid="classMsg" kindref="compound">Msg</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
